		<Paragraph>
			NeoEdit is a powerful text editor that allows finding and editing multiple selections, in multiple files, visually, at the same time.
		</Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>
			To get best results, you'll want to mainly use the keyboard. The mouse works, but it can't really handle multiple selections at once.
		</Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>
			The major focuses of the program are selecting and editing. There are many ways to select the data you want to change, and many ways to edit that data.
